      <p>Greater Manchester Homelessness Action Network (GMHAN) brings together people with personal insight into homelessness, people from frontline organisations, public sector and others to find more effective solutions. For updates about homelessness in Greater Manchester, join our <a href="https://streetsupport.us12.list-manage.com/subscribe?u=da9a1d4bb2b1a69a981456972&id=3c6ae13085">mailing list</a>.</p>
      <h2 class="h2">Covid-19 crisis response</h2>
      <p>During the current Covid-19 crisis, we're working together at GMHAN to co-ordinate an effective response. There will be regular information circulated via our <a href="http://streetsupport.us12.list-manage1.com/subscribe?u=da9a1d4bb2b1a69a981456972&id=52ba96f2af">mailing list</a> and we will be collating different perspectives from across the network.</p>
      <p>There is co-ordination at Greater Manchester level with each Local Authority leading on their locality response. For specific information about your borough, select it from the box below. General updates will be posted on our <a href="https://news.streetsupport.net/tag/greater-manchester/">news section</a>.</p>
