      <h2 class="h2">A Bed Every Night</h2>
      <p>Rough sleeping is the most visible form of homelessness. In Greater Manchester we aim to find solutions so that no-one needs to sleep on the streets.</p>
      <p>Throughout the year local authorities and the voluntary sector work hard to prevent
        and reduce homelessness, but resources are stretched - there are not enough houses and support. Over the winter, we are responding to this crisis by providing emergency provision across the region, and we need your help!</p>
